Beast Tongue		KEY:Juju Mystery ~ Beast Tongue						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:JujuRevelation.OracleRevelation.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																							DESC:You can communicate with a single type of animal (birds, cats, snakes, fish, and so on) as if you were constantly using speak with animals. Although this ability grants you the ability to converse with such creatures, it grants you no special influence over them.																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.14
Connaissance		KEY:Juju Mystery ~ Connaissance						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:JujuRevelation.OracleRevelation.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																							DESC:You can spend a full-round action to attune yourself to the spirit world, gaining the benefit of a moment of prescience spell with a +%1 insight bonus. You may use this ability %2 times per day, but you may only have one connaissance effect active at a time.|max(1,floor(OracleLVL/2))|max(1,CHA)																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.14
Ensnare the Soul		KEY:Juju Mystery ~ Ensnare the Soul						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:JujuRevelation.OracleRevelation.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																							DESC:Your magic turns others into zombielike servants. Add charm person and dominate person to your spell list. Creatures affected by either spell become listless and pale, appearing dead to observers (DC 20 Heal or Perception check to determine the creature is not undead). Affected creatures are slow to take any action unless you specifically direct them to do so. They are not mindless or helpless, however, and defend themselves if attacked.																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.15	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=1|Charm Person	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=5|Dominate Person
Juju Senses			KEY:Juju Mystery ~ Juju Senses						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:JujuRevelation.OracleRevelation.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																							DESC:When casting detect magic and identify, you gain a +2 bonus on Knowledge (arcana) and Spellcraft checks to recognize auras and identify their properties. You also gain a +2 bonus on Perception and Sense Motive checks made against spirit creatures, such as outsiders, fey, and incorporeal undead. At 10th level, this bonus increases to +4.																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.15
Night Terror		KEY:Juju Mystery ~ Night Terror						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:JujuRevelation.OracleRevelation.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	PRECLASS:1,Oracle=11																																			DESC:You send your spirit to torment another being's dreams. Once per day, you may target a creature with the effects of a nightmare spell. Instead of the spell's normal damage, you make a full attack, using your Charisma modifier in place of your Strength modifier, against the victim's touch AC. You deal 1d10 damage for each successful hit.																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.15
Path of the Snake		KEY:Juju Mystery ~ Path of the Snake					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:JujuRevelation.OracleRevelation.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	PRECLASS:1,Oracle=11																																			DESC:Once per day, |PREVARLT:OracleLVL,11	DESC:Twice per day, |PREVARGTEQ:OracleLVL,11	DESC:as a standard action, you can become incorporeal. While in this form, you gain a +10 bonus on Stealth checks and can move in any direction and through any object (except for those made of force). You can take no action other than to move while in this form. You remain in this form for %1 rounds, but you can end this effect prematurely with a standard action.|OracleLVL																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.15
Spiritual Defense		KEY:Juju Mystery ~ Spiritual Defense					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:JujuRevelation.OracleRevelation.SpecialQuality.SpellLike																																							DESC:Your chanting grants protection against your enemies. As a move action, you can begin chanting to gain the benefit of a protection spell (such as protection from evil) using your oracle level as your caster level. This protection lasts until you stop chanting or for the spell's normal duration, whichever comes first. Chanting after the initial round of the effect is a free action, and you can incorporate verbal components and communication into the chant; magical silence ends a chant and its protection effect.	DESC:You can chant aloud to create a magic circle effect (such as magic circle against evil). |PREVARGTEQ:OracleLVL,6	DESC:You can use this ability %1 times per day.|CHA+3																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.15
Summon Nature's Spirits	KEY:Juju Mystery ~ Summon Nature's Spirits				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:JujuRevelation.OracleRevelation.SpecialQuality.SpellLike	PRECLASS:1,Oracle=5																																			DESC:Once per day, as a standard action, you may cast a summon monster spell of a level up to the highest level you can cast. You may only summon elementals in this manner, but are treated as having the Augment Summoning feat when you do so.																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.15
Unwilling Host		KEY:Juju Mystery ~ Unwilling Host						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:JujuRevelation.OracleRevelation.SpecialQuality.SpellLike	PRECLASS:1,Oracle=7																																			DESC:You command spirits to invade the bodies of your enemies. Once per day as a standard action you may target %1 creatures within lOO feet, no two of which can be more than 30 feet apart. Targeted creatures must make a Will save or suffer the effects of a confusion spell as the spirits possess them and cause them to behave erratically for %2 rounds.|CHA|OracleLVL																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.15
Final Revelation		KEY:Juju Mystery ~ Final Revelation						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:JujuRevelation.OracleRevelation.SpecialQuality																																									DESC:At 20th level, you become a master of the connections between the mortal world and the spirit world. Your knowledge enables you to gain incredible insight and control over others by manipulating spiritual energy. You gain a +%1 insight bonus to your AC and on all saving throws and Knowledge checks. Additionally, once per day, you may cast extended dominate monster as a spell-like ability. With this ability, you may dominate %2 creatures.|CHA|CHA*2																																																																																																																																			BONUS:COMBAT|AC|CHA|TYPE=Insight	BONUS:SAVE|ALL|CHA|TYPE=Insight	BONUS:SKILL|TYPE.Knowledge|CHA|TYPE=Insight																						SOURCEPAGE:p.15

