Priest-Blessed		KEY:Trait ~ Priest-Blessed							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait										PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Priest-Blessed]							DESC:Three times per day when you are the target of a harmless divine spell, you may increase its caster level by 1 for purposes of its effect on you alone.																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.33
Proxy of Many		KEY:Trait ~ Proxy of Many							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait										PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Proxy of Many]							DESC:You gain a +2 trait bonus on Diplomacy checks made to request a favor from a creature that has not performed a favor for you in the past week. This bonus increases to +4 if you have performed a favor for that creature since it last did a favor for you.																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.33
Religious Reformer	KEY:Trait ~ Religious Reformer						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait										PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Religious Reformer]						DESC:You gain a +2 trait bonus on Knowledge (religion) checks that pertain to your own religion or spiritual practice, and you gain a +2 trait bonus on saving throws against spells cast by others who worship your god or adhere to your philosophy.																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.33
Self-Actualization	KEY:Trait ~ Self-Actualization						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait										PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Self-Actualization]						DESC:Once per day, when you take 20 on a roll or check, you can complete the action in only five times the normal amount of time for that action, rather than 20 times the normal amount.																																																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.33
Totemist			KEY:Trait ~ Totemist								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait										PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Totemist]								DESC:Once per day, you may call upon your totem's wisdom as a standard action. You gain the benefits of guidance, except that the granted competence bonus is +(max(1,floor(CASTERLEVEL/2))). This is a supernatural ability.																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.33
Traditionalist		KEY:Trait ~ Traditionalist							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait										PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Traditionalist]							DESC:You gain a +1 trait bonus on Knowledge (history) and Knowledge (local) checks, and one of those skills (your choice) becomes a class skill for you.																																																																																											STACK:NO	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:SKILL|Knowledge (History)|Knowledge (Local)																																																																																											BONUS:SKILL|Knowledge (History),Knowledge (Local)|1|TYPE=Trait							CSKILL:LIST											SOURCEPAGE:p.33
Wendifa Apprentice	KEY:Trait ~ Wendifa Apprentice			NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait										PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Wendifa Apprentice]						DESC:You can use daze as a spell-like ability once per day, using your character level as your caster level (minimum 1). The save DC of this effect is Charisma-based. The dazed individual looks ashen and deathly for the duration of the effect.																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.33
Zealot's Bearing		KEY:Trait ~ Zealot's Bearing							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait										PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Zealot's Bearing]							DESC:You gain a +2 bonus on Diplomacy and Intimidate checks when dealing with adherents of your faith or philosophy, but a -1 penalty on Diplomacy and Intimidate checks when dealing with anyone else.																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.33
